---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="体験談・成果｜IB専門家庭教師IBT"
  description="IBTで学んだ生徒たちの体験談と成果をご紹介。IB卒業生講師による専属担当制の個別指導で、生徒一人ひとりが成長しています。"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "ホーム", "item": "https://ib-tutors.net/" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "体験談・成果", "item": "https://ib-tutors.net/results/" }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ibt-gradient-start via-ibt-gradient-mid to-ibt-gradient-end py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-white/85 text-sm mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">ホーム</a>
        <span class="mx-2">&gt;</span>
        <span class="text-white">体験談・成果</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">IBTで成長した生徒たち</h1>
      <p class="text-white/80 mt-3 text-lg">IB卒業生講師の専属指導で、一人ひとりが確実に成長しています。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IBTの強み概要 -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-ibt-bg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <p class="text-ibt-red font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">WHY STUDENTS GROW</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold">IBT生徒が成長する理由</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">専属担当制</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">体験授業から最終試験まで同じ講師が担当。学習の流れが途切れません。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">IB卒業生講師</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">講師全員がIB修了者。経験に基づく的確なアドバイスで生徒を導きます。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">オーダーメイド指導</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">一人ひとりの目標・弱点に合わせた完全個別カリキュラムで効率的に学べます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 受講生の声 -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <p class="text-ibt-red font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">STUDENT VOICES</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold">受講生の声</h2>
        <p class="text-ibt-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">IBTで学んだ生徒たちのリアルな声をお届けします。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- 体験談プレースホルダー 1 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-bg rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-ibt-gradient-start to-ibt-gradient-end rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">--</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-ibt-text">イニシャル（準備中）</p>
              <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm">プログラム: ---</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed italic border-t border-ibt-border pt-4">"受講生の体験談を準備中です。"</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 体験談プレースホルダー 2 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-bg rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-ibt-gradient-start to-ibt-gradient-end rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">--</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-ibt-text">イニシャル（準備中）</p>
              <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm">プログラム: ---</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed italic border-t border-ibt-border pt-4">"受講生の体験談を準備中です。"</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 体験談プレースホルダー 3 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-bg rounded-2xl border border-ibt-border p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-ibt-gradient-start to-ibt-gradient-end rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">--</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-ibt-text">イニシャル（準備中）</p>
              <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm">プログラム: ---</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed italic border-t border-ibt-border pt-4">"受講生の体験談を準備中です。"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-ibt-text-light/60 text-xs mt-8">※ 受講生の許可を得て掲載しています</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-ibt-bg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ibt-gradient-start via-ibt-gradient-mid to-ibt-gradient-end rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">あなたも無料体験から始めてみませんか?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-8 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
          60分の無料体験で、IB卒業生講師の指導を実感してください。お子さまに合った講師をご紹介します。
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="inline-block bg-white text-ibt-red font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-ibt-red-light transition-colors text-lg shadow-lg"
        >
          60分無料体験に申し込む
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
